Package com.i2group.apollo.adminservice.transport

Contains classes for communicating information with the service that administers a deployment of i2 Analyze.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RepositoryNameResult
    A container for a String that contains the human-readable name of an Analysis Repository.
    SchemaResult
    A container for an i2 Analyze Schema.
    SecuritySchemaResult
    A container for an i2 Analyze SecuritySchema.
